data.description: Spacious living with some unique amenities. Solar panels keeping electrical bills at a minimum. Luxury vinyl plank flooring in kitchen and dining area, tray ceiling in kitchen, vaulted ceilings, sauna, large walk-in closet, exercise area with equipment included, pellet stove and a wood stove. New 50 yr roof in 2022, covered patio, close to reservoir (fishing is allowed) and there is a trail to the beach.
